44
00:05:20,030 --> 00:05:22,480
Don't joke around like this anymore.

45
00:05:22,480 --> 00:05:26,610
I was never fooling, not ten years ago and not now.

46
00:05:27,490 --> 00:05:30,860
I liked you then, and I like you now.

47
00:05:39,220 --> 00:05:42,720
