Rethink it carefully starting now.

60
00:06:31,050 --> 00:06:33,310
Are we really just friends?

61
00:06:33,310 --> 00:06:41,900
♫  I always want to be by your side  ♫

62
00:07:01,220 --> 00:07:04,980
Is Lee Ddoong having fun with Kang Hu Yeong?

63
