218
00:19:06,890 --> 00:19:10,340
Who's the "Carp Head"?

219
00:19:11,700 --> 00:19:13,040
I don't know.

220
00:19:13,040 --> 00:19:17,150
   

221
00:19:17,150 --> 00:19:19,500
   

222
00:19:19,500 --> 00:19:22,440
Why is everyone doing this to me?

223
00:19:22,440 --> 00:19:25,560
What are you saying? Finish eating first.

224
00:19:30,290 --> 00:19:36,270
Hey, I ate pork. Why does it taste like onion?

225
00:19:37,960 --> 00:19:42,710
Hong Ju, I think there's a crack in your head.

226
00:19:42,710 --> 00:19:43,920
Are you okay?

227
00:19:43,920 --> 00:19:45,260
Let go.

228
00:19:45,260 --> 00:19:46,920
Okay.

229
00:19:47,900 --> 00:19:50,360
Hu Yeong will be here in a while.

230
00:19:50,360 --> 00:19:52,240
Oh, why?

231
00:19:53,100 --> 00:19:54,340
To eat!

232
00:19:54,340 --> 00:19:57,830
Geez! Who said you could invite him?

233
00:19:57,830 --> 00:20:01,780
Why can't I invite my friend to my restaurant? What?

234
00:20:01,780 --> 00:20:04,780
I can't eat comfortably because of Kang Hu Yeong.

235
00:20:04,780 --> 00:20:06,420
Hey, hey.

236
00:20:06,420 --> 00:20:08,750
Hey, hey, hey.

237
00:20:11,160 --> 00:20:13,080
Hong Ju, I'll put this on your tab!

238
00:20:13,080 --> 00:20:16,640
-  Okay!  
 - It's 37,000 won ($27)!

239
00:20:19,340 --> 00:20:22,950
 Here's the soju you ordered. 

240
00:20:30,690 --> 00:20:32,810
 Hey. 

241
00:20:32,810 --> 00:20:35,700
She ran away as if debt collectors were after her.

242
00:20:35,700 --> 00:20:38,130
Is it a fight or a fling?

243
00:20:41,410 --> 00:20:43,700
Okay.

244
00:20:43,700 --> 00:20:46,900
Is it my turn to step in?

245
00:20:46,900 --> 00:20:48,640
What?

246
00:20:51,510 --> 00:20:59,010
 Bus numbers 6716 and 603 are arriving soon. 

247
00:21:05,630 --> 00:21:08,590
   
   

248
00:21:26,450 --> 00:21:30,300
 Hey, Kang Hu Yeong! Wait right there. I'll be right over. 

249
00:21:30,300 --> 00:21:32,100
 Wait. 

250
00:21:42,480 --> 00:21:45,950
Oh, it was then.

251
00:21:48,570 --> 00:21:51,800
Wow, why do I remember that?

252
00:21:51,800 --> 00:21:54,140
Gosh, Kwon Sang Pil, that jerk.

253
00:21:54,140 --> 00:21:57,410
He made an injured person peel all those onions.

254
