256
00:22:19,760 --> 00:22:23,430
Black... What?

257
00:22:30,950 --> 00:22:33,360
"No color..."

258
00:22:34,150 --> 00:22:38,250
"can change the color black."

259
00:22:39,080 --> 00:22:45,300
"That's why my love for you is black, Oppa."

260
00:22:45,300 --> 00:22:48,380
"It will never change..."

261
00:22:52,700 --> 00:22:56,400
How could the color black change?

262
00:23:11,810 --> 00:23:13,820
What?

263
00:23:15,560 --> 00:23:19,110
Did you just change, too?

264
00:23:19,110 --> 00:23:22,680
You said the color black lasts forever.

265
00:23:22,680 --> 00:23:25,090
